text: Kihniö is a municipality in Pirkanmaa, Finland. As of 28 February 2023, 1,765 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Kurikka, Parkano, Seinäjoki, Virrat and Ylöjärvi. Most people speak Finnish. == Other websites == * Municipality of Kihniö – Official website Category:Municipalities of Pirkanmaa
